 |archive-date = 2015-11-24
 |dead-url = yes
 }}</ref>，拥有约6000名译者<ref>[[translatewiki:Special:Statistics|Statistics]], 2 August 2014.</ref>及来自超过20个项目的50000页面<ref>{{cite web
