== 功能 ==

translatewiki.net是一个[[wiki|wiki]]站点，因此任何网络用户都可以很方便地作出贡献，而几乎无[[准入门槛|障碍]]<ref name=celebrates>{{cite web
 |first1 = Niklas
 |last1 = Laxström
 |title = translatewiki.net celebrates – so do I
 |url = http://laxstrom.name/blag/2011/04/22/translatewiki-net-celebrates-so-do-i/
 |accessdate = 2014-08-02
 |date = 2011-04-22
 |archive-date = 2014-08-08
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808045147/http://laxstrom.name/blag/2011/04/22/translatewiki-net-celebrates-so-do-i/
 |dead-url = no
 }}，庆祝建站6周年。</ref>。译者可以专注做他们最擅长的事——翻译，没有其它烦恼，从而确保了翻译的品質。

翻译立即对译者可用，并会流畅地同步[[版本控制|版本控制]]系统和可翻译的wiki页面<ref>{{cite web
 |title = Translatewiki.net Community
 |url = http://mifosx.openmf.org/Mifos%20website/mifos.org/community/spotlight/translatewikinet-community.html
 |website = mifos.openmf.org
 |accessdate = 2014-11-01
 |date = 2011-04-27
 |quote = The switch to Translatewiki.net provides us with a stable and actively maintained translation infrastructure smoothly syncing with our Git repository
 |archive-date = 2014-08-08
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808043024/http://mifosx.openmf.org/Mifos%20website/mifos.org/community/spotlight/translatewikinet-community.html
 |dead-url = no
 }}</ref>，无需译者的干预。在最好的情况下，对于维基媒体计划使用的MediaWiki，新的[[本地化|本地化]]内容在[[mw:Localisation#Update_of_localisation|一天之内]]就能同步至网站上。

翻译编辑器提供了各种[[電腦輔助翻譯|電腦輔助翻譯]]功能，如
* 消息文档，也称为“上下文”，
* 来自[[语料库|语料库]]和[[机器翻译|机器翻译]]的建议，
* 检查翻译中常见的语法错误，
* 消息的翻译状态。<ref name=tux>{{cite web|url=http://blog.wikimedia.org/2013/03/25/redesigning-the-translation-experience-an-overview/|date=2013-03-25|title=Redesigning the Translation experience: An overview|work=Wikimedia Foundation blog|accessdate=2014-11-01|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611121220/http://blog.wikimedia.org/2013/03/25/redesigning-the-translation-experience-an-overview/|dead-url=no}}{{unreliable source|date=2014年12月}}</ref>

